<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 00:32:43 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>哈马斯接受停火协议后，内塔尼亚胡面临关键时刻</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-faces-his-moment-of-truth-after-hamas-accepts-ceasefire-deal/0000018f-4fee-dc9e-a7df-4ffe493a0000</link><description>以色列总理很可能不想在此时达成协议，但地面入侵拉法的威胁也有可能成为对哈马斯的最后筹码。一位参与谈判的官员表示，“如果内塔尼亚胡想要达成协议，这或多或少是他能达成的最好协议”</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 22:38:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-faces-his-moment-of-truth-after-hamas-accepts-ceasefire-deal/0000018f-4fee-dc9e-a7df-4ffe493a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列在加沙是否违反了国际法？布林肯本周必须回答的关键问题</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-06/ty-article/.premium/blinken-must-answer-by-wednesday-is-israel-complying-with-international-law-in-gaza/0000018f-4df5-d17f-adcf-fdf791dc0000</link><description>随着以色列违背美国意愿准备对拉法采取地面行动，而以色列和哈马斯正在逐步接近达成停火和人质协议，美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯必须在周三之前告诉国会他是否接受以色列的保证使用美国武器时不得违反国际法</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 20:02:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-05-06/ty-article/.premium/blinken-must-answer-by-wednesday-is-israel-complying-with-international-law-in-gaza/0000018f-4df5-d17f-adcf-fdf791dc0000</guid></item><item><title>“令我惊讶的是到目前为止它是如何做到的”：巴勒斯坦人对以色列关闭半岛电视台的反应</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-05-06/ty-article/.premium/surprising-they-managed-until-now-palestinians-react-to-israels-shutdown-of-al-jazeera/0000018f-4dbd-dd3a-a5cf-7ffff8250000</link><description>在以色列关闭卡塔尔拥有的新闻网络的当地办事处后，巴勒斯坦人批评该禁令是为了掩盖其对加沙战争的密集报道</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 19:24:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-05-06/ty-article/.premium/surprising-they-managed-until-now-palestinians-react-to-israels-shutdown-of-al-jazeera/0000018f-4dbd-dd3a-a5cf-7ffff8250000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯戏剧性地接受停火是否会导致以色列的拉法计划失败？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-06/ty-article/.highlight/does-hamas-dramatic-cease-fire-acceptance-doom-israels-rafah-plan/0000018f-4eeb-d346-afef-7fff93af0000</link><description>现在将有新一轮的指控和反指控，以色列将“研究”细节，并可能再次派出谈判小组前往开罗。但与此同时，以色列军队不会进入拉法</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 19:13:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-06/ty-article/.highlight/does-hamas-dramatic-cease-fire-acceptance-doom-israels-rafah-plan/0000018f-4eeb-d346-afef-7fff93af0000</guid></item><item><title>对于内塔尼亚胡来说，那永远是 1938 年，美国大学校园都是纳粹德国</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-06/ty-article/.premium/for-netanyahu-its-always-1938-and-u-s-college-campuses-are-nazi-germany/0000018f-4dbc-d17f-adcf-fdffc7ff0000</link><description>任何熟悉本杰明·内塔尼亚胡 (Benjamin Netanyahu) 对历史的解释的人都不应该对他最近将美国大学校园的亲巴勒斯坦抗议活动与 20 世纪 30 年代的德国进行可笑的比较感到惊讶</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 15:52:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-06/ty-article/.premium/for-netanyahu-its-always-1938-and-u-s-college-campuses-are-nazi-germany/0000018f-4dbc-d17f-adcf-fdffc7ff0000</guid></item><item><title>“我们正在应对正在发生的性大屠杀”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-06/ty-article-magazine/.premium/were-dealing-with-a-sexual-shoah-as-its-happening/0000018f-4e07-d6c3-afdf-4f5707650000</link><description>在全球抗议加沙战争的背景下（其中一些抗议还否认哈马斯系统性性犯罪），以色列电影制片人阿纳特·斯大林斯基（Anat Stalinsky）于 10 月 7 日通过前 Meta 首席运营官谢丽尔·桑德伯格（Sheryl Sandberg）的采访制作了一部记录性暴力的电影</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 15:33:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-06/ty-article-magazine/.premium/were-dealing-with-a-sexual-shoah-as-its-happening/0000018f-4e07-d6c3-afdf-4f5707650000</guid></item><item><title>联合国指责以色列拒绝向加沙提供援助以避免饥荒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-06/ty-article/un-accuses-israel-of-denying-aid-access-to-gaza-in-its-efforts-to-avert-famine/0000018f-4e00-dd3a-a5cf-7f77fa590000</link><description>虽然负责协调加沙援助的以色列国防军单位 COGAT 表示，国际组织表示有太多援助进入加沙北部，但近东救济工程处负责人菲利普·拉扎里尼坚称，检查站的援助运送仍然存在长时间延误，枪击事件车队和逮捕联合国工作人员</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 15:00:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-06/ty-article/un-accuses-israel-of-denying-aid-access-to-gaza-in-its-efforts-to-avert-famine/0000018f-4e00-dd3a-a5cf-7f77fa590000</guid></item><item><title>土耳其贸易抵制：对以色列经济打击有多大？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/business/2024-05-06/ty-article/.premium/turkeys-boycott-how-big-a-blow-to-israels-economy/0000018f-4df5-dd3a-a5cf-7ff718e50000</link><description>一个主要担忧是，如果以色列进入拉法，埃尔多安因加沙战斗而抵制贸易的行为可能会蔓延到其他国家</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 14:50:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/business/2024-05-06/ty-article/.premium/turkeys-boycott-how-big-a-blow-to-israels-economy/0000018f-4df5-dd3a-a5cf-7ff718e50000</guid></item><item><title>比利时试图拉拢欧洲国家对以色列实施经济制裁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-05-06/ty-article/.premium/belgium-trying-to-recruit-european-countries-to-impose-economic-sanctions-on-israel/0000018f-4de3-d17f-adcf-fde3aad60000</link><description>据比利时报道，总理亚历山大·德克鲁 (Alexander De Croo) 告诉助手，“我认为我们不能继续将以色列视为贸易伙伴” ■ 此举的可能合作伙伴可能是爱尔兰、卢森堡和马耳他，这些国家一直被自战争爆发以来对以色列非常批评</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 14:18:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-05-06/ty-article/.premium/belgium-trying-to-recruit-european-countries-to-impose-economic-sanctions-on-israel/0000018f-4de3-d17f-adcf-fde3aad60000</guid></item><item><title>制定道德准则并不能阻止纳粹医生犯下战争罪</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-06/ty-article-magazine/.premium/having-an-ethics-code-didnt-stop-nazi-doctors-from-committing-war-crimes/0000018f-49b8-d6c3-afdf-4dfb2b7c0000</link><description>从对数十万人进行绝育到医学实验和杀害有特殊需要的人：以色列教授什穆埃尔·雷斯告诉《国土报》，世界各地的医学院应该如何教授这一残酷的历史篇章</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 12:38:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-06/ty-article-magazine/.premium/having-an-ethics-code-didnt-stop-nazi-doctors-from-committing-war-crimes/0000018f-49b8-d6c3-afdf-4dfb2b7c0000</guid></item><item><title>无人机在梅图拉爆炸；作为回应，以色列国防军袭击了真主党的精锐拉德万部队目标</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-06/ty-article/.premium/thirty-rockets-fired-at-israels-north-by-hezbollah-drone-explodes-in-metula/0000018f-4d4c-dd3a-a5cf-7f7feeb20000</link><description>周一早些时候，三枚火箭从黎巴嫩向戈兰高地发射，对房屋造成轻微损坏。以色列军队评估称，此次袭击是对以色列国防军夜间袭击黎巴嫩深处真主党大院的回应</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 11:05:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-06/ty-article/.premium/thirty-rockets-fired-at-israels-north-by-hezbollah-drone-explodes-in-metula/0000018f-4d4c-dd3a-a5cf-7f7feeb20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列欧洲电视网代表出席大屠杀纪念仪式而不是开幕活动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-06/ty-article/.premium/israeli-eurovision-singer-attends-holocaust-memorial-ceremony-instead-of-opening-event/0000018f-4d60-d17f-adcf-fde3f8020000</link><description>出于安全考虑，戈兰和她的团队此前曾表示，除了排练和她的实际表演之外，他们不会参加任何欧洲歌唱大赛的活动。周日，这位以色列歌手在马尔默犹太社区举行的小型大屠杀纪念仪式上点燃了蜡烛</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 10:50:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-06/ty-article/.premium/israeli-eurovision-singer-attends-holocaust-memorial-ceremony-instead-of-opening-event/0000018f-4d60-d17f-adcf-fde3f8020000</guid></item><item><title>加沙医疗消息人士称，以色列在地面行动之前开始撤离，拉法有 26 人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-06/ty-article/.premium/israel-begins-evacuation-of-civilians-from-rafah-defense-chief-says-hamas-left-no-choice/0000018f-4cf7-dcda-abcf-6ef708a20000</link><description>以色列国防军估计，加沙南部社区约有10万居民被勒令撤离，但军方消息人士称，这只是有限行动，并没有完全撤离拉法</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 10:15:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-06/ty-article/.premium/israel-begins-evacuation-of-civilians-from-rafah-defense-chief-says-hamas-left-no-choice/0000018f-4cf7-dcda-abcf-6ef708a20000</guid></item><item><title>在加沙拥挤的战场上，许多以色列士兵被友军炮火打死</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-06/ty-article/.premium/on-gazas-crowded-battlefields-many-israeli-soldiers-are-killed-by-friendly-fire/0000018f-4cee-d414-a5bf-ffff3da30000</link><description>上周，两名预备役军人在加沙被以色列坦克炮火误认为敌人而身亡。一名中队指挥官就该事件表示：“以我们现有的手段，这种情况可能会再次发生”</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 09:24:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-06/ty-article/.premium/on-gazas-crowded-battlefields-many-israeli-soldiers-are-killed-by-friendly-fire/0000018f-4cee-d414-a5bf-ffff3da30000</guid></item><item><title>十年前的以色列法律可能会阻碍与黎巴嫩真主党的冲突缓和</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-06/ty-article/.premium/a-decade-old-israeli-law-could-hamper-deescalation-with-hezbollah-in-lebanon/0000018f-4cb7-d414-a5bf-ffb73eb60000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡政府2014年通过的一项法律规定，任何以色列领土的割让都必须经过全民公投或议会多数席位的批准，这可能会影响总理确保以色列北部与黎巴嫩边境保持平静的能力</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 09:01:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-06/ty-article/.premium/a-decade-old-israeli-law-could-hamper-deescalation-with-hezbollah-in-lebanon/0000018f-4cb7-d414-a5bf-ffb73eb60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列通过敬献花圈和大屠杀纪念馆纪念大屠杀纪念日</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-06/ty-article/.premium/israel-marks-holocaust-remembrance-day-with-wreath-laying-yad-vashem-ceremony/0000018f-4c7d-d414-a5bf-ff7fa1560000</link><description>随着警报声使国家陷入停顿，全国各地将举行仪式。周日晚上，内塔尼亚胡在大屠杀纪念馆举行的一次活动中表示，“即使我们必须孤立无援，我们也将继续与人类的邪恶作斗争”</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 06:24:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-06/ty-article/.premium/israel-marks-holocaust-remembrance-day-with-wreath-laying-yad-vashem-ceremony/0000018f-4c7d-d414-a5bf-ff7fa1560000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯谈判濒临崩溃，内塔尼亚胡摆出了拒绝主义的姿态</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-06/ty-article/.premium/with-hamas-talks-on-the-verge-of-collapse-netanyahu-puts-up-a-rejectionist-front/0000018f-4a51-d6c3-afdf-4f530dfb0000</link><description>中央情报局局长被派往中东，努力挽救人质协议，而内塔尼亚胡被认为是主要障碍。美国压力的大小将决定他是否答应拜登总统的要求</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 03:02:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-06/ty-article/.premium/with-hamas-talks-on-the-verge-of-collapse-netanyahu-puts-up-a-rejectionist-front/0000018f-4a51-d6c3-afdf-4f530dfb0000</guid></item><item><title>关闭半岛电视台是以色列搬起石头砸自己的脚</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-06/ty-article/.premium/by-shutting-down-al-jazeera-israel-is-shooting-itself-in-the-foot/0000018f-4a76-dcda-abcf-6a77785b0000</link><description>通过关闭卡塔尔新闻网络，以色列加入了一个由阿拉伯国家组成的杰出俱乐部，该俱乐部已经停止了半岛电视台的运营。此举应该令以色列媒体感到担忧，因为以色列媒体被禁止在加沙地带内部独立进行广播</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 03:01:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-06/ty-article/.premium/by-shutting-down-al-jazeera-israel-is-shooting-itself-in-the-foot/0000018f-4a76-dcda-abcf-6a77785b0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯接受停火协议，以色列“审查”提议；以色列国防军进入拉法</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-06/ty-article-live/idf-three-soldiers-killed-near-gaza-border/0000018f-4ba4-dcda-abcf-6ba7979b0006</link><description>哈马斯表示已接受停火协议，以色列表示仍在审查该提议 ■ 以色列国防军在拉法以东发动有针对性的袭击 ■ 拜登、内塔尼亚胡讨论拉法行动 ■ 白宫：协议是拯救人质生命的最佳方式，内塔尼亚胡同意重新开放凯雷姆沙洛姆过境点</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 02:30:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-06/ty-article-live/idf-three-soldiers-killed-near-gaza-border/0000018f-4ba4-dcda-abcf-6ba7979b0006</guid></item><item><title>以色列中部和北部夜间发生枪击事件，两名男子丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-06/ty-article/.premium/two-men-killed-in-overnight-shootings-in-central-and-northern-israel/0000018f-4bfe-dcda-abcf-6bff97570000</link><description>警方怀疑至少其中一起事件与有组织犯罪有关</description><pubDate>Sun, 05 May 2024 21:51:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-06/ty-article/.premium/two-men-killed-in-overnight-shootings-in-central-and-northern-israel/0000018f-4bfe-dcda-abcf-6bff97570000</guid></item></channel></rss>